_Hina Safdar_ at _Chowrangi_ [urges](http://www.chowrangi.com/earth-
hour-2010-switch-off-the-lights-to-play-your-part.html) Pakistanis to switch
off lights in honor of [earth hour](http://www.earthhour.org/) tonight at 8:30
PM when hundreds of cities around the world will switch off the lights for 60
minutes.

